Diagnosis. SIF = 7B-B-3-2111.0000; fsp = 7.7.7; fCx = 1.1.1; fSt = 2.2; fPp = N/N/BNN; fSc: PL> AM> AL; Ip = 601–625; fD = 2H-8-6-6-2-2; DS = 26–28;
V = 23–24; NDV = 49–52. Standard measurements of type series given in Table 1
